Description: In this package we provide code as helper functions 
  to build precision matrix for spatial and spatial models.
  The objects are to be used along the 'INLA' package. 
  The model setup are designed to build the needed data 
  in order to use the 'cgeneric' interface provided by 'INLA'.
  The implemented functions include the spatial barrier model, 
  see Bakka et. al. (2019) <doi:10.1016/j.spasta.2019.01.002>,
  and spatio-temporal models, see Lindgren et. al. (2023) 
  <arXiv:2006.04917>. 
  Details are provided in the available vignettes 
  from the provided link
